nodes.text: Star Wars 20 is the twentieth and final issue of the Legends comic book series Star Wars. It was written by Brian Wood, illustrated by Carlos D'Anda and Gabe Eltaeb, and first published by Dark Horse Comics on August 13, 2014.
Leia risks it all for a friend she hasn't seen since childhood! Han, Luke, and Chewie risk it all for Leia!
Brian Wood and Carlos D'Anda say farewell to that galaxy far, far away before they send our heroes to an unknown fate!
